revision.text:
{{sbarinfo|[not] <value>}}


Executes the following sub block if the player's [[Swimming#Waterlevel|waterlevel]] is greater than or equal to {{c|value}}. If {{c|not}} is provided, the check is inverted, and the sub block is executed if the player's waterlevel is less than {{c|value}}.

== Examples ==
This block of code is executed if the player is completely submerged in water.
 IfWaterLevel 3
 {
   // commands...
 }


This one, however, is executed if the player is not submerged at all.
 IfWaterLevel not 1
 {
   // commands...
 }
